						<summary>

						<p>States that <hi rend="bold">Goṅgula Pōchi-Nāyaka,</hi> a dependent of General <hi rend="bold">Rudradēva,</hi> made a gift of land to the temple Vaṅkēśvaradēva of <hi rend="bold">Dugya</hi> (Durgi). The general is said to be ruling the land.</p>						

